Name: Pointer tool

Synonyms: Pointer tool,Arrow tool

Type: glossary

Description:
<Tool> used in the LiveCode <development environment> to select, move, and resize <control|controls>. 
 
When the Pointer tool is being used, the <cursor> is in the shape of an arrow.

References: development environment (glossary), tool (glossary), cursor (glossary), control (glossary)
